('Finance & Operations', 'Featured Expert - Small Business Trends with Rieva Lesonsky ', '<p>The environment in which small business operates is constantly changing.&nbsp; Global trends such as social media usage and mobile information access are now affecting small business owners in a big way&mdash;making their world smaller and more competitive.</p>\r\n<p>Listen to this podcast with Rieva Lesonsky and our Business Accelerator Host, Euan Ford, as Rieva discusses some of the business trends that small business owners are facing today.&nbsp; See how technology innovation such as mobile marketing is becoming a must-do for many small business owners if they wish to succeed in the very near future.</p>\r\n<p>Be sure to also read Rieva&rsquo;s articles on how to address the growing pains involved in running a small business in our fast-changing environment.</p>\r\n<p>Next steps to complete this chapter:</p>\r\n<p>Consider which trends you think are a must for you to follow in order to assure business growth.</p>', 'http://www.kaltura.com/index.php/kwidget/cache_st/1333032834/wid/_737192/uiconf_id/7642702/entry_id/1_3d0m92sz'),
('Finance & Operations', 'Featured Expert - Stever Robbins podcast ', '<p>How would life change if you committed to living only a life that you defined as &ldquo;extraordinary?&rdquo;&nbsp; As an entrepreneur, we may pursue &ldquo;extraordinary&rdquo; in our careers, but completely forget our personal lives&mdash;foregoing any balance and harmony between work and the life we lead outside of it.</p>\r\n<p>This chapter will include a podcast with Stever Robbins and our Business Accelerator Host, Euan Ford, as Stever discusses how entrepreneurs can grow their business, yet maintain work/life balance.&nbsp; Listen in as Stever addresses the age-old myth that entrepreneurs have to devote their entire lives to the business.</p>\r\n<p>Be sure to also read Stever&rsquo;s articles included in this chapter on leading your team and your small business to new levels of success.</p>\r\n<p>Next steps to complete this chapter:</p>\r\n<p>Consider whether or not you are satisfied with your work/life balance.</p>', 'http://www.kaltura.com/index.php/kwidget/cache_st/1333033006/wid/_737192/uiconf_id/7642702/entry_id/1_jym5ixso'),
