('Leadership & Growth', 'The Pain-Free Business Plan for Those Who Seek Long-Term Success ', '<p>Having a business plan is paramount to your long-term growth. A good business plan conveys the excitement and promise of your business to any potential backer or future stakeholder. In this webinar, with Michael Valentine, The Plan Doctor, learn how to craft a professional. Master the ability to create, amend, or rework your small business plan&mdash;without the headache.</p>\r\n<p>In this chapter, learn:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A fresh new blueprint to approach the continuous growth of your businesses</li>\r\n<li>Why having a well-tailored business plan will lead you to where you want to go</li>\r\n<li>How to construct a business plan you&rsquo;ll actually use</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://amfam.webex.com/amfam/lsr.php?AT=pb&SP=EC&rID=47572922&rKey=a2570f147d33cac7 '),
