('Sales', 'Featured Expert - Social Media for Small Business with John Jantsch', '<p>When used properly, social media can be a great tool to help your business reach untapped, potential customers and stay connected to current ones.&nbsp; But there are a few things you&rsquo;ll need to know to help you get the most out of social media marketing as well as your online presence in its entirety.</p>\r\n<p>In this chapter, John Jantsch--small business expert and author of <em>Duct Tape Marketing</em> and <em>The Referral Engine</em>&mdash;will break social media down into easy-to-understand pieces so you can make sense of and make use of this powerful resource in a way that grows your business.</p>\r\n<p>Listen to John&rsquo;s podcast with Business Accelerator Host, Euan Ford, for some quick tips on leveraging social media in your business.&nbsp; Be sure to read John&rsquo;s articles and e-book <em>Let&rsquo;s Talk: Social Media for Small Business</em> for further understanding.</p>\r\n<p>Next steps to complete this chapter:</p>\r\n<p>Take an hour one evening to read John Jantsch&rsquo;s ebook, <em>Let&rsquo;s Talk: Social Media for Small Business.&nbsp; </em>Decide which activities you can deploy and make your to-do list.</p>', 'http://www.kaltura.com/index.php/kwidget/cache_st/1333032875/wid/_737192/uiconf_id/7642702/entry_id/1_l1muo00z'),
