('Sales', 'LinkedIn Level II ', '<p>Are you comfortable with LinkedIn but you want to learn how to use it even more effectively to generate appointments?&nbsp;&nbsp; In this chapter, Dean DeLisle will take your LinkedIn learning to the next level.&nbsp; He&rsquo;ll teach you how to tune up your LinkedIn profile for maximum impact&mdash;both with your connections and with SEO.&nbsp; He&rsquo;ll show you how you can use LinkedIn&rsquo;s search capabilities to find prospects in your target audience and add connections to magnify your network to millions quickly.&nbsp; Finally, Dean will discuss the importance of recommendations and how you must both give and get them to truly leverage the power of LinkedIn.</p>\r\n<p>Be sure to download the handouts in this chapter to help you set up your profiles and give you ideas on how to ask for an appointment with LinkedIn connections.</p>\r\n<p>Next steps to complete this chapter:</p>\r\n<p>Ask 5 five of your connections in LinkedIn to give you a recommendation.&nbsp; Be sure to take the time to write a recommendation back.</p>', 'https://amfam.webex.com/amfam/lsr.php?AT=pb&SP=EC&rID=41226497&rKey=47cabef1a6167866 '),
