('Leadership & Growth', 'Build a Team for Business Growth ', '<p><strong>Note:</strong> Start at 46:34</p>\r\n<p>You launched your small business with excitement, energy, and a staff of one, or maybe two. You&rsquo;ve made it past your one year anniversary and know you have something to offer. You&rsquo;re ready to turn some of your attention to growing your business but need some additional resources. How do you know when to build your team?</p>\r\n<p>In this chapter, we&rsquo;ll explore the common questions that small business owners struggle with when figuring out how to grow their company.&nbsp; Should you add a full-time person, part-timers, or interns? How can you create a virtual board to support you in your growth and success?</p>\r\n<p>Small business owners have a lot of options for building their team. Whether you are ready to build now or planning for it down the road, in this chapter you&rsquo;ll explore the many paths available and what might fit for you.</p>\r\n<p>Next steps to complete this chapter:</p>\r\n<p>Create a list of the additional support you need to support your business growth.</p>', 'https://amfam.webex.com/amfam/lsr.php?AT=pb&SP=EC&rID=43195317&rKey=ef217fa3db532f41 '),
('Sales', 'Discover how to increase your book of business with the new 2013 edition of LinkedIn', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;"><span style="color: #1f497d; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">Dean DeLisle, our social media coach,&nbsp;&nbsp;gives you the Top Business Development Techniques and covers newly released 2013&nbsp;features in LinkedIn. This is a "Game Changer" for online Social Networking!&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;"><span style="color: #1f497d; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;"><span style="color: #1f497d; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">With over 200,000,000 professionals on LinkedIn, you are closer to your targeted sales prospects than you think. Learn how to find them before your competitors do. You will also see what it takes to get THEM to find YOU &ndash; all while using LinkedIn less than 20 minutes a day! </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;"><span style="color: #1f497d; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="f